{"id":239537,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/07/维权网-河北访民刘海满被以非法上访劳教（图）/","date":"2012-07-12T18:30:47Z","modified":"2012-07-12T18:30:47Z","title":"维权网 | 河北访民刘海满被以非法上访劳教（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div><span> </span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><br /><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员厉荣泉报道）本网信息员获悉，河北省秦皇岛市青龙满族自治县三拨子乡二拨子村村民刘海满，男，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">49</span><span>岁，因到京上访，被当地政府以非正常上访劳教一年，期间受尽各种折磨虐待</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>月份劳教所领导说签息诉罢访就放你</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span><span>可</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">25</span><span>日</span><span>签完后至今没有放人。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>刘海满由于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2009</span><span>年机动车肇事赔偿案，于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">17</span><span>日</span><span>到北京上访，被户口所在地青龙县三拨子乡政府李会刚、王金明、张红奎、张秀峰等人接回之后的十多天家属都没有刘海满的下落，经家属多方寻找才得知刘海满在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18</span><span>日上午</span><span>被青龙县公安局法制科以扰乱社会治安罪送往秦皇岛市海港区劳动教养所教养</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>年，家属迄今没有得到公安机关的任何电话与书面通知。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>  </span></span></div>\n<div><span>刘海满身患脑梗、脑血栓、心脏病、高血压等疾病，几近生活不能自理（有秦皇岛第一医院与北京武警总队医院病历本与诊断书），公安机关与劳教所双方都知道刘海满是一位这样病人的前提下，在没有对病人做任何体检的情况下，将他关押在秦皇岛市海港区劳教所。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>秦皇岛市青龙县公安局践踏法律违反劳教法规，打击报复上访人</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span><span>没有为刘海满做任何的体检</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span><span>伪造体检表</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span><span>将丧失劳动能力的上访人送进劳教所</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span><span>后逼签息诉罢诉，竟然又迟迟不释放刘海满，可见秦皇岛劳教部门违法侵权的情况。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-bO6vWi7t3qE/T_70kW4zL_I/AAAAAAAAJNs/nWxVyhWZWbE/s1600/20120710_3.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-bO6vWi7t3qE/T_70kW4zL_I/AAAAAAAAJNs/nWxVyhWZWbE/s320/20120710_3.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-2237062443558981692?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/07/f1bba5a220120710_3.jpg-150x150.jpg\" /></p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18269,20534],"tags":[16910]}